maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 3 Evening” game were:
5-9-7, Wild: 1
(five, nine, seven; Wild: one)
